{"type": "article", "id": 30810, "title": "扶手椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-09T23:01:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160809233236QXbZw78I3hjf2usJ.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>瑞典设计师 Karoliina Priha 与来自墨西哥的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/kalebjcardenasz\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kaleb J Cardenas Z</a> 共同设计了这把被命名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/9839527/Cool-Chair\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cool Chair</a> 的扶手椅，它最大的特点在于由管状靠垫交叠而成的椅背，就像是童话书中的海浪。Priha 在制作靠垫时选用了传统填充物马鬃毛，织物表面则由羊毛制成，这两种天然材料的组合保证了椅背的柔软舒适。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608092332589pk0euDNhlACWxYs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233300Ln3HcPXsw59qECli.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233258x9VqXcI1siY5NbuT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233304kdJVUfnm0chiCzqL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}